KitKat:;

She looked at Cooley, "But, you are a Decepticon. The ones who came 
before the predacon. The ones whose programs goevern ours. We 
fashioned our existance from you. How can you say that your just a 
plain anything. You are the ones whom the predacons are decended. You 
are the orignal rulers. The ones who first fought the Autobots. From 
there, we eventually took up the battle in the name of Decepticon 
rule."

She sighed at this new world around her. She looked at her glass and 
wondered why she ever wondered how her and a bot like Blackfang could 
ever get along. She let her mind wander for a moment and wondered if 
he even ever gave her a second thought.
